Subject: [PATCH] Add Starter/Growth/Custom engagement tier cards to all 5
 service pages

- Reuses existing .offer-card shell and .offer-card--lead highlight modifier
- New .tier-feature-list CSS for the bullet list inside each card (uses --space, --sage tokens)
- Inserted between 'How It Works' and 'Proof' sections on each page
- Copy sourced from Brand Hub nested offers (AI Workflow System, Government Growth System,
  Business Command Center, Launch the Brand) and built first as a Figma component set
